153
00:08:38,750 --> 00:08:44,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How dare you show your face to me 
after pulling a stunt like that?!</font>

154
00:08:44,500 --> 00:08:45,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We need to talk.</font>

155
00:08:45,850 --> 00:08:46,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me?</font>

156
00:08:46,630 --> 00:08:48,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Talk?!</font>

157
00:08:48,300 --> 00:08:52,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You dug up your mother's grave 
and pissed on her reputation!</font>

158
00:08:52,970 --> 00:08:56,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're a scumbag who'll stoop 
to anything to make it big!</font>

159
00:08:56,310 --> 00:08:58,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why the hell would 
I give you the time of day?!</font>

160
00:08:59,670 --> 00:09:00,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because...</font>

161
00:09:01,290 --> 00:09:06,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know the name of the guy 
who masterminded Ai's death.</font>

162
00:09:07,940 --> 00:09:10,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You what? Ai's killer?</font>

163
00:09:10,900 --> 00:09:12,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who is it? Spit it out!</font>

164
00:09:12,420 --> 00:09:13,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't.</font>

165
00:09:13,740 --> 00:09:16,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I tell you, you'll try 
to go kill him right now.</font>

166
00:09:16,900 --> 00:09:17,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn right I will!</font>

167
00:09:18,140 --> 00:09:21,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you really wanna let that bastard 
go scot-free after all he did?!</font>

168
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:24,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like hell I do.</font>

169
00:09:25,750 --> 00:09:29,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Killing him would be letting him off easy.</font>

170
00:09:32,670 --> 00:09:34,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's your game?</font>

171
00:09:34,730 --> 00:09:38,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you trying to do 
by telling me this?</font>

172
00:09:40,150 --> 00:09:43,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been thinking about it 
ever since I was a kid.</font>

173
00:09:44,780 --> 00:09:47,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's the best way to get revenge 
on the man who killed Ai?</font>

174
00:09:48,110 --> 00:09:51,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How can I make him suffer the most?</font>

175
00:09:52,500 --> 00:09:55,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I took all my hatred 
and put it down in words,</font>

176
00:09:56,220 --> 00:09:59,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">creating a rough draft that was 
like a child's temper tantrum—</font>

177
00:09:59,500 --> 00:10:02,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">a completely selfish and reckless plan.</font>

178
00:10:03,920 --> 00:10:04,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However...</font>

179
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:08,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ever since I learned 
how Ai felt about it all,</font>

180
00:10:08,740 --> 00:10:11,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've gained all the cards I needed 
to build the perfect hand.</font>

181
00:10:12,770 --> 00:10:17,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This plan could've never come 
to pass without a miracle,</font>

182
00:10:17,920 --> 00:10:21,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but now everything's fallen 
into place to make it possible.</font>

183
00:10:22,640 --> 00:10:24,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I've got no choice but to run with it.</font>

184
00:10:25,570 --> 00:10:27,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The curtain's already risen 
on the final act.</font>

185
00:10:28,210 --> 00:10:32,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The moment Ai's story went public, 
there was no going back for me.</font>

186
00:10:33,980 --> 00:10:35,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want your help.</font>

187
00:10:36,400 --> 00:10:39,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Help me drive that man into a corner.</font>

188
00:10:40,200 --> 00:10:42,660
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="32"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#362823">Gotanda Studio</font></font></font></b></font>

189
00:10:40,200 --> 00:10:42,660
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="40"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#251d19">GOTANDA</font></font></font></b></font>

190
00:10:42,660 --> 00:10:46,670
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="30"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#53494e">Ai</font></font></font></b></font>

191
00:10:44,400 --> 00:10:46,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Ai Hoshino.</font>

192
00:10:47,070 --> 00:10:50,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your kids are living strong.</font>

193
00:11:05,470 --> 00:11:10,480
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="13"><font face="Times New Roman">Pitch</font></font></b></font>

194
00:11:05,470 --> 00:11:10,480
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="15"><font face="Times New Roman">The 15-Year Lie
<font size="13">(Tentative Title)</font></font></font></b></font>

195
00:11:11,430 --> 00:11:14,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It might be time to make good 
on that promise.</font>

196
00:11:13,490 --> 00:11:16,950
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="13"><font face="Times New Roman">Pitch</font></font></b></font>

197
00:11:13,490 --> 00:11:16,950
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="15"><font face="Times New Roman">The 15-Year Lie
<font size="13">(Tentative Title)</font></font></font></b></font>

198
00:11:23,660 --> 00:11:25,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, wow!</font>

199
00:11:25,760 --> 00:11:27,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He fell asleep?</font>

200
00:11:30,960 --> 00:11:33,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get this log off me and take him home.</font>

201
00:11:33,950 --> 00:11:37,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way. I wanna watch this some more.</font>

202
00:11:37,180 --> 00:11:38,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?</font>

203
00:11:38,590 --> 00:11:41,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because Aqua never takes 
to people like this.</font>

204
00:11:41,930 --> 00:11:45,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe he thinks 
you're his dad or something.</font>

205
00:11:45,320 --> 00:11:49,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please stop. That cuts deep for 
a guy who's still single at thirty.</font>

206
00:11:53,400 --> 00:12:00,370
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><font color="#4a1b10"></font></font></b>The Beginning</font>

207
00:11:54,240 --> 00:11:58,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You wrote this story yourself, right?</font>

208
00:11:58,240 --> 00:12:00,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The script was a great read 
all on its own!</font>

209
00:12:00,370 --> 00:12:02,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How do you write stuff like this?</font>

210
00:12:03,280 --> 00:12:04,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

211
00:12:05,070 --> 00:12:09,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the end, it all comes down 
to whether it's got real emotion.</font>

212
00:12:09,990 --> 00:12:11,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For this movie,</font>

213
00:12:11,750 --> 00:12:15,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that'd be the lead's inferiority complex 
and her desire to be beautiful.</font>

214
00:12:15,710 --> 00:12:19,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't half-ass that stuff 
in favor of the plot.</font>

215
00:12:20,350 --> 00:12:21,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have to film what's real.</font>

216
00:12:22,750 --> 00:12:26,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's really the only thing 
that matters in filmmaking.</font>

217
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:32,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Though of course, it takes technique 
to make that more appealing.</font>

218
00:12:32,990 --> 00:12:34,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow.</font>

219
00:12:34,590 --> 00:12:37,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's kinda amazing. 
You're a real professional.</font>

220
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:38,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Duh.</font>

221
00:12:39,730 --> 00:12:40,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I know!</font>

222
00:12:40,830 --> 00:12:45,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My agency's been talking about 
filming a B-Komachi documentary.</font>

223
00:12:45,450 --> 00:12:48,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should make it, Director!</font>

224
00:12:48,210 --> 00:12:50,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Why me?</font>

225
00:12:50,590 --> 00:12:53,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">'Cause I feel like you'd 
make a real good one.</font>

226
00:12:53,790 --> 00:12:55,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll do it, right?</font>

227
00:12:55,840 --> 00:12:58,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't be silly. I've got enough 
on my plate already.</font>

228
00:12:58,840 --> 00:13:01,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, come on! Please?</font>

229
00:13:01,130 --> 00:13:01,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like I said...</font>

230
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:03,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll do it, right?</font>

231
00:13:03,680 --> 00:13:04,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wrong.</font>

232
00:13:04,430 --> 00:13:05,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pretty please?</font>

233
00:13:05,810 --> 00:13:08,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For the last time, I'm not doing it!</font>

234
00:13:35,880 --> 00:13:37,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>After that,</i></font>

235
00:13:37,560 --> 00:13:41,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I filmed the original B-Komachi's 
documentary bit by bit.</i></font>

236
00:13:41,720 --> 00:13:44,930
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="36"><i><font face="Georgia"><font color="#e90056">B-Komachi</font></font></i></font></b></font>

237
00:13:41,720 --> 00:13:44,930
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="36"><i><font face="Georgia"><font color="#e90056">B-Komachi</font></font></i></font></b></font>

238
00:13:42,060 --> 00:13:44,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We'd finalized the screening schedule.</i></font>

239
00:13:44,920 --> 00:13:48,640
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="18"><font color="#2e2729">B-Komachi Moved to Tears As First Tokyo Dome Concert Is Announced</font></font></b></font>

240
00:13:44,930 --> 00:13:47,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Shooting the Tokyo Dome concert 
was all that was left.</i></font>

241
00:13:49,810 --> 00:13:51,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But that was when...</i></font>

242
00:13:51,690 --> 00:13:55,610
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font color="#0a0a0a">B-Komachi's Ai-san Attacked by Fan</font></b></font>

243
00:13:51,690 --> 00:13:55,610
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font color="#0a0a0a">Dead</font></b></font>

244
00:13:51,690 --> 00:13:55,610
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="15"><font color="#0a0a0a">Idol Group B-Komachi's</font></font></b></font>

245
00:13:51,690 --> 00:13:55,610
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font color="#0a0a0a">Ai<font color="#0a0a0a">-san</font></font></b></font>

246
00:13:52,780 --> 00:13:54,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>the murder happened.</i></font>

247
00:13:55,830 --> 00:13:59,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ai was killed, 
and everything got scrapped.</i></font>

248
00:14:00,860 --> 00:14:03,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I heard that as Ai was dying, 
she asked the boy wonder</i></font>

249
00:14:03,580 --> 00:14:05,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>to apologize to "the director" for her.</i></font>

250
00:14:06,670 --> 00:14:09,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm the one who should apologize.</i></font>

251
00:14:10,830 --> 00:14:17,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I may have been one of the few adults 
who could've reached out to help her.</i></font>

252
00:14:23,380 --> 00:14:28,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sheesh. I haven't filmed a documentary 
since I was in school.</font>

253
00:14:28,910 --> 00:14:30,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen up.</font>

254
00:14:30,270 --> 00:14:33,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I'm doing this, I'm not 
making something shoddy.</font>

255
00:14:34,150 --> 00:14:36,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're gonna put up a front</font>

256
00:14:36,520 --> 00:14:40,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or show a version of you that's 
made up of lies like you always do,</font>

257
00:14:40,600 --> 00:14:43,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't hesitate to cancel 
filming on the spot.</font>

258
00:14:44,540 --> 00:14:48,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess you did say 
you wanted to film what's real.</font>

259
00:14:49,370 --> 00:14:51,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But are you sure?</font>

260
00:14:52,730 --> 00:14:55,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you film me when 
I'm not being a total liar,</font>

261
00:14:55,180 --> 00:14:57,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you probably won't be able 
to use any of the footage.</font>

262
00:14:58,860 --> 00:15:00,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're okay with that,</font>

263
00:15:01,200 --> 00:15:03,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">then I won't lie.</font>

264
00:15:06,140 --> 00:15:08,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please film the real me.</font>

265
00:15:14,020 --> 00:15:16,020
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="40"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#222021">The 15-Year Lie</font></font></font></b></font>

266
00:15:14,020 --> 00:15:16,020
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="30"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#222021">Script</font></font></font></b></font>

267
00:15:15,670 --> 00:15:19,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A movie based on a real-life incident?</font>

268
00:15:20,150 --> 00:15:21,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The script's pretty much finished.</font>

269
00:15:22,980 --> 00:15:26,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An idol shoots to stardom</font>

270
00:15:26,020 --> 00:15:29,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and is killed by a fan on the day 
of her Tokyo Dome concert.</font>

271
00:15:31,010 --> 00:15:35,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did it happen, and what was 
going on behind the scenes?</font>

272
00:15:37,960 --> 00:15:39,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ai-kun, huh?</font>

273
00:15:39,520 --> 00:15:40,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

274
00:15:41,030 --> 00:15:45,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a movie based on a true story: 
the murder of an idol fourteen years ago.</font>

275
00:15:46,310 --> 00:15:49,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll bring it to life 
using today's actors.</font>

276
00:15:55,190 --> 00:15:59,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pretty intriguing story you've got here, 
but it'll be hard to pull off.</font>

277
00:16:00,770 --> 00:16:05,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The subject matter is far too delicate, 
and too much of it's based on speculation.</font>

278
00:16:05,950 --> 00:16:07,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you have anything to back this up?</font>

279
00:16:08,300 --> 00:16:12,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're not careful, this could get you 
sued by a bunch of places.</font>

280
00:16:12,450 --> 00:16:16,790
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="18"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#4c383a">Pitch
<font size="24">The 15-Year Lie</font></font></font></font></b></font>

281
00:16:12,450 --> 00:16:16,790
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="18"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#4c383a">Script
Taishi Gotanda
Aqua Hoshino</font></font></font></b></font>

282
00:16:13,530 --> 00:16:16,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No major film distributors 
or investors will take this on.</font>

283
00:16:17,160 --> 00:16:19,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You won't get the funding required.</font>

284
00:16:19,950 --> 00:16:21,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry to say this project—</font>

285
00:16:21,540 --> 00:16:22,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can back it all up.</font>

286
00:16:24,110 --> 00:16:27,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's based on an account from Ai herself.</font>

287
00:16:29,470 --> 00:16:32,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's more, the script 
was written by the director</font>

288
00:16:32,930 --> 00:16:35,590
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="32"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#2a2620">Script</font></font></font></b></font>

289
00:16:33,510 --> 00:16:38,640
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="32"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#2a2620">Taishi Gotanda
Aqua Hoshino</font></font></font></b></font>

290
00:16:33,960 --> 00:16:37,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and Ai's actual son, me.</font>

291
00:16:40,890 --> 00:16:44,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I get it. So that's what you're going for.</font>

292
00:16:45,430 --> 00:16:50,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">While I do get the feeling that you're 
taking Gotanda-kun and me for a ride...</font>

293
00:16:50,490 --> 00:16:53,450
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font size="40"><font color="#1f1d1b">Lie</font></font></font></b></font>

294
00:16:51,720 --> 00:16:53,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From how you describe it,</font>

295
00:16:54,030 --> 00:16:55,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">this could get interesting.</font>

296
00:16:57,090 --> 00:16:58,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Very</i> interesting.</font>

297
00:17:00,910 --> 00:17:04,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Very well. I'll take this movie on.</font>

298
00:17:05,790 --> 00:17:09,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the only one who could produce it.</font>

299
00:17:11,760 --> 00:17:14,470
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="24"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#302a2a">Pitch
<font size="34">The 15-Year Lie</font></font></font></font></b></font>

300
00:17:11,760 --> 00:17:14,470
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="24"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#302a2a">Script
Taishi Gotanda
Aqua Hoshino</font></font></font></b></font>

301
00:17:12,150 --> 00:17:14,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The cast I have in mind for starters is...</font>

302
00:17:15,110 --> 00:17:16,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ruby Hoshino,</font>

303
00:17:16,750 --> 00:17:17,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">MEMcho,</font>

304
00:17:17,720 --> 00:17:18,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kana Arima,</font>

305
00:17:18,980 --> 00:17:20,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Melt Narushima,</font>

306
00:17:20,480 --> 00:17:22,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Frill Shiranui,</font>

307
00:17:22,230 --> 00:17:23,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Akane Kurokawa,</font>

308
00:17:23,980 --> 00:17:25,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Taiki Himekawa,</font>

309
00:17:26,100 --> 00:17:28,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and Aqua Hoshino.</font>

310
00:17:30,400 --> 00:17:31,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go with that for now.</font>

311
00:17:31,950 --> 00:17:34,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who do we want for Ai, the lead role?</font>

312
00:17:34,990 --> 00:17:38,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's gotta be a huge box-office draw.</font>

313
00:17:38,150 --> 00:17:41,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I do have someone in mind.</font>

314
00:17:42,200 --> 00:17:44,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yura Katayose-san.</font>

315
00:17:44,360 --> 00:17:48,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you be willing to let us 
book her schedule for next spring?</font>

316
00:17:48,370 --> 00:17:53,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, we have gotten other offers,</font>

317
00:17:53,070 --> 00:17:56,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but you've always been 
good to us, Kaburagi-san.</font>

318
00:17:56,180 --> 00:17:58,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guarantee she'll have a leading role.</font>

319
00:17:59,630 --> 00:18:00,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Very well.</font>

320
00:18:00,850 --> 00:18:02,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excited to work with you next spring.</font>

321
00:18:03,560 --> 00:18:05,520
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#3f281e">Members Only</font></font></b></font>

322
00:18:03,560 --> 00:18:05,520
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="28"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#cacbcc">Maru-chan Bar</font></font></font></b></font>

323
00:18:08,480 --> 00:18:12,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It all just rubs me 
the wrong way, I swear!</font>

324
00:18:12,370 --> 00:18:15,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get me another Maru-chan special!</font>

325
00:18:15,170 --> 00:18:16,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

326
00:18:16,450 --> 00:18:20,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, what would your fans 
think if they saw this?</font>

327
00:18:20,410 --> 00:18:27,500
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="25"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#1346a0">Actor
<font color="#020202">Yura Katayose</font></font></font></font></b></font>

328
00:18:20,900 --> 00:18:23,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The biggest and hottest 
actress right now,</font>

329
00:18:23,600 --> 00:18:25,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">getting wasted like this?</font>

330
00:18:27,740 --> 00:18:30,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, work just gets me so stressed.</font>

331
00:18:31,590 --> 00:18:33,800
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font color="#5b171f">TV <font color="#cdb249">Guidance</font></font></font></b></font>

332
00:18:31,590 --> 00:18:33,800
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font color="#c6607e">TV <font color="#cdb249">Guidance</font></font></font></b></font>

333
00:18:31,590 --> 00:18:33,800
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="10"><font color="#a15619">\hSpecial
Feature</font></font></b></font>

334
00:18:31,590 --> 00:18:33,800
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font size="20"><font color="#7a0a26">Yura
Katayose</font></font></font></b></font>

335
00:18:32,750 --> 00:18:35,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I don't blow off steam 
somewhere, I'll explode!</font>

336
00:18:33,800 --> 00:18:36,010
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="18"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#f0f1e9">If you're looking for a home, come to <font color="#f8c884">HOMESHOP</font></font></font></font></b></font>

337
00:18:33,800 --> 00:18:36,010
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="16"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#f0f1e9">Now Taking Tenant Applications</font></font></font></b></font>

338
00:18:37,040 --> 00:18:41,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take today, for example. 
My manager brought me this movie role.</font>

339
00:18:41,190 --> 00:18:45,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But they just booked my schedule. 
Everything else is up in the air.</font>

340
00:18:45,480 --> 00:18:49,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, but isn't that pretty 
common with TV series?</font>

341
00:18:49,560 --> 00:18:51,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure, but this is a movie.</font>

342
00:18:52,340 --> 00:18:56,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Neither my manager nor the producer 
are treating me with the care I deserve.</font>

343
00:18:56,900 --> 00:19:00,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It feels like all they care about 
is my brand value and fame.</font>

344
00:19:00,950 --> 00:19:03,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know that's not true.</font>

345
00:19:03,110 --> 00:19:07,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're pretty, and it's amazing 
how much your acting's come along.</font>

346
00:19:07,070 --> 00:19:10,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you! You really are 
the best drinking buddy, Miki-san!</font>

347
00:19:10,790 --> 00:19:11,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">C'mon, drink up!</font>

348
00:19:11,830 --> 00:19:13,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, damn.</font>

349
00:19:14,080 --> 00:19:19,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everything that producer offers me 
is an adaptation targeting a younger demo.</font>

350
00:19:19,840 --> 00:19:23,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm twenty-five now. I can't pull off 
a school uniform anymore.</font>

351
00:19:23,700 --> 00:19:27,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They should be giving those parts 
to actual high schoolers.</font>

352
00:19:27,810 --> 00:19:31,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like, isn't Frill Shiranui 
still in high school?</font>

353
00:19:31,780 --> 00:19:35,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And recently, there's... You know...</font>

354
00:19:35,300 --> 00:19:36,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ruby Hoshino!</font>

355
00:19:36,870 --> 00:19:38,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's all the rage right now.</font>

356
00:19:38,660 --> 00:19:42,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, her? I've got my eye on her, too.</font>

357
00:19:42,700 --> 00:19:44,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Knew it!</font>

358
00:19:44,050 --> 00:19:46,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She must be getting 
a ton of offers right now.</font>

359
00:19:46,860 --> 00:19:49,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's always a demand for pretty faces.</font>

360
00:19:50,560 --> 00:19:55,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bet the showrunners 
would rather use younger actors, too.</font>

361
00:19:56,460 --> 00:20:03,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They just come to me because nobody 
that age is a big enough box-office draw.</font>

362
00:20:05,690 --> 00:20:10,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But, well, I refuse to just 
be their crowd puller.</font>

363
00:20:10,930 --> 00:20:12,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a wonderful mindset.</font>

364
00:20:15,660 --> 00:20:16,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You see...</font>

365
00:20:17,300 --> 00:20:20,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to become a better actor 
and a bigger name,</font>

366
00:20:20,950 --> 00:20:24,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and free myself from 
all these business obligations.</font>

367
00:20:25,550 --> 00:20:27,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll act in great movie after great movie,</font>

368
00:20:27,790 --> 00:20:33,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and play the lead in a masterpiece that'll
be talked about a century from now!</font>

369
00:20:34,510 --> 00:20:36,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you think I could do it?</font>

370
00:20:37,590 --> 00:20:42,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your talent is the real deal. 
It has that kind of staying power.</font>

371
00:20:42,100 --> 00:20:43,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

372
00:20:43,740 --> 00:20:45,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you have the day off tomorrow?</font>

373
00:20:46,030 --> 00:20:46,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup.</font>

374
00:20:47,490 --> 00:20:53,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Every time I finish a big job, I make a 
point of taking a month off to unwind.</font>

375
00:20:53,730 --> 00:20:56,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going mountaineering next week.</font>

376
00:20:56,820 --> 00:20:58,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've gotten hooked on it lately.</font>

377
00:20:58,600 --> 00:21:01,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See? I have an app to keep track 
of the mountains I've hiked.</font>

378
00:21:02,900 --> 00:21:05,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's lovely. I like the mountains, too.</font>

379
00:21:06,830 --> 00:21:08,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be careful, though.</font>

380
00:21:09,230 --> 00:21:11,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the mountains,</font>

381
00:21:11,470 --> 00:21:13,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they might never find you 
if something goes wrong.</font>

382
00:21:16,230 --> 00:21:19,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be sure to watch your step.</font>

383
00:21:31,130 --> 00:21:32,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you still alive?</font>

384
00:21:33,420 --> 00:21:34,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I warned you...</font>

385
00:21:35,190 --> 00:21:37,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to watch your step.</font>

386
00:21:40,630 --> 00:21:43,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You... murderer...</font>

387
00:21:50,660 --> 00:21:53,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Her light's gone out.</font>

388
00:21:56,330 --> 00:21:59,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've gone and extinguished another one,</font>

389
00:22:01,210 --> 00:22:02,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ai!</font>

390
00:22:06,550 --> 00:22:09,930
<font face="Times New Roman" size="32" color="#0a0a0a"><b>{\an8}Episode 32










